{"tid":976092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NASA將測試太空船撞小行星 以期拯救人類","createTime":"2019-01-10T07:05:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-10T13:02:51.000Z","uid":184679,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"8c9dac96c57fe809cc93db626e9edc61be17754c","tid":976092,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:05:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/01/DART.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FDART.jpg&h=c04f524c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國太空總署（NASA）計劃發射太空船撞擊不具威脅的小行星，使其行進方向發生偏移，以測試這種方法的可行性，以便將來若有小行星將撞上地球時，可以採用此法化解危機，以拯救人類的性命。<br />\n<br />\n這項行星捍衛任務被稱為「雙小行星轉向測試」（Double Asteroid Redirection Test，DART）。有別於NASA的大多數太空船都是用來進行探勘，這項任務所發射的太空船將用來撞擊小行星。<br />\n<br />\nDART的撞擊目標為Didymos（在希臘語中指「雙胞胎」），它是個雙小行星系統，由一大一小的小行星組成，而DART的太空船將撞擊比較小的那顆小行星。<br />\n<br />\n這兩顆小行星分別被稱為Didymos A和Didymos B。前者較大，有780米寬，而後者較小，其寬度為160米，它環繞著Didymos A運轉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2019/01/DART-1-600x377.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FDART-1-600x377.jpg&h=62351157&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">DART的太空船預定在2022年10月撞擊Didymos B。（NASA）</span><br />\n<br />\n自從2003年開始，科學家就一直在研究Didymos這個雙小行星系統。DART項目的科學家施塔特勒（Tom Statler）表示：「雙小行星系統是進行這項測試的絕佳天然實驗室。」<br />\n<br />\n施塔特勒說，由於Didymos B繞行Didymos A，科學家更容易觀察太空船撞擊的結果，並確保這項測試不會改變它們環繞太陽的軌道。<br />\n<br />\nDART的太空船在發射之後，將會飛向Didymos，並使用自動化的系統來瞄準Didymos B，進而在預定的時間撞擊它。<br />\n<br />\n如果DART任務如期在2021年6月展開的話，那這艘雪櫃大小的太空船預定在2022年10月撞上Didymos B，其撞擊速度高達每秒3.7哩（每秒6公里），相當於子彈速度的9倍左右。而地球上的望遠鏡將被用來觀測本次撞擊所產生的結果。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，這樣的撞擊只會使目標小行星的速度改變一點點，但隨著時間的推移，它的改變會累加起來，足以使小行星的行進路徑偏離地球。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-01-08/58752801\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2019-01-08%2F58752801&d=LthhP1B6BQ%2FTlQrjY2XBYtr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=ad127556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2019-01-08/58752801</a>"},{"pid":"d56481b60d6356ffa7b7118a2afbfb7ef5de551f","tid":976092,"uid":41204,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:18:28.000Z","msg":"美國佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d8310de9e84da2c2325862395b8d9f843f5ab7","tid":976092,"uid":14918,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"撞小行星落支那is ok"},{"pid":"ee176767b7aac4dbdc9e2f02fc9a19fe8e38bcb6","tid":976092,"uid":182499,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:28:31.000Z","msg":"計錯數就冚球家剷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da4728f9381df04d1d01a522f40cbbb67c3e1eaf","tid":976092,"uid":759,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"一陣地心住左外星人<br />\n撞埋去即係開戰"},{"pid":"d56613a6471813276e4dd9881d725092dbb6d791","tid":976092,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:31:45.000Z","msg":"cherk到有貴金屬就噴佢落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1489f47e4ff584fcf9eed4c5ca4e673ed704f93","tid":976092,"uid":34010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:32:30.000Z","msg":"呢d野揾阿寶去做就得啦"},{"pid":"f6e6381aa721a272eef161e30e8a88126cbd4703","tid":976092,"uid":144529,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:33:43.000Z","msg":"小行星撞到落黎會冚球剷咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50c3b4d976589444a4a8edce82a82454980aaa79","tid":976092,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d8310de9e84da2c2325862395b8d9f843f5ab7","tid":976092,"uid":14918,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:26:00.000Z","msg":"撞小行星落支那is ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-10T07:35:20.00